title: Living Under Divine Protection | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Living Under Divine Protection | Joel Osteen
description:
It’s easy to worry and live in fear, but you have to remember, you are never alone. As you keep God first place, He will keep you under HIs supernatural protection. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
